 Another way, let's say here in login,

135
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,520
 we're gonna get the login URL

136
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,840
 and send ourselves back to the request path.

137
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:36,240
 Request is another one of these things

138
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,560
 that's dropped in automatically for us.

139
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:41,800
 That is the current URL of the view we're at.

140
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:45,880
 So, in a sense, this is a contraction that says,

141
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,360
 go ahead and go to login,

142
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,360
 and when you're back, come right back here.

143
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:52,720
 So, login will login and then redirect back to this page

144
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,760
 that we're on, whatever the page is.

